name: Christy Mack (pre MMA)
description:
Christy Mack

The Pre-MMA version. I ran across a short film with Christy while doing >cough< research and wanted to put something together. There is another embedding of her on the site already from a few months ago. I hope this is a good compliment to that one.

I ran it against v1.4 at a 3e-03 rate and this is the 9000 step model.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
